@startuml
!theme plain
title SMEV3 Adapter Service - Data Flow Sequence Diagram

actor Client
participant "API Layer\n(views.py)" as API
participant "QueryProcessor\n(query.py)" as Processor
participant "Adapter\n(adapter.py)" as Adapter
participant "Loader\n(schema_loader)" as Loader
participant "Model\n(models.py)" as Model
database "MongoDB" as DB
participant "SMEV3\nAdapter\n(SOAP)" as SMEV3

== Query Scheduling Flow ==

Client -> API: POST /schedule_query/<query_type>/
activate API

API -> Loader: Load XSD schema for query_type
activate Loader
Loader --> API: Return schema
deactivate Loader

API -> API: Validate request against XSD schema
API -> Model: Create Query object
activate Model
Model -> DB: Insert query document
activate DB
DB --> Model: Query ID
deactivate DB
Model --> API: Query object with ID
deactivate Model

API -> Processor: Schedule query processing
activate Processor

Processor -> Adapter: Send request to SMEV3
activate Adapter

Adapter -> Loader: Get XSD schema
activate Loader
Loader --> Adapter: Schema definition
deactivate Loader

Adapter -> Adapter: Construct SOAP message\nusing zeep
Adapter -> SMEV3: SOAP request (SendRequestRequest)
activate SMEV3
SMEV3 --> Adapter: SOAP response with MessageId
deactivate SMEV3

Adapter --> Processor: MessageId
deactivate Adapter

Processor -> Model: Update query with MessageId
activate Model
Model -> DB: Update query document
activate DB
DB --> Model: Success
deactivate DB
deactivate Model

Processor --> API: Query scheduled
deactivate Processor

API --> Client: HTTP 200 with Query ID
deactivate API

== Background Response Polling ==

Processor -> Processor: Periodic task triggered
activate Processor

Processor -> Adapter: Poll for responses (GetResponseRequest)
activate Adapter

Adapter -> SMEV3: SOAP request (GetResponseRequest)
activate SMEV3
SMEV3 --> Adapter: SOAP response with documents
deactivate SMEV3

Adapter -> Loader: Get response XSD schema
activate Loader
Loader --> Adapter: Schema definition
deactivate Loader

Adapter -> Adapter: Parse and validate response\nusing lxml and zeep
Adapter --> Processor: Parsed response data
deactivate Adapter

Processor -> Loader: Get document XSD schema
activate Loader
Loader --> Processor: Schema definition
deactivate Loader

Processor -> Processor: Validate document against schema

Processor -> Model: Create document model instance\nusing create_model factory
activate Model

Model -> DB: Insert document
activate DB
DB --> Model: Document ID
deactivate DB

deactivate Model

Processor -> Model: Update query status
activate Model
Model -> DB: Update query document
activate DB
DB --> Model: Success
deactivate DB
deactivate Model

deactivate Processor

== Document Retrieval Flow ==

Client -> API: GET /get_document/<query_type>/<query_id>/
activate API

API -> Model: Retrieve document by query_id
activate Model
Model -> DB: Query document collection
activate DB
DB --> Model: Document data
deactivate DB
Model --> API: Document object
deactivate Model

API -> Loader: Get document XSD schema
activate Loader
Loader --> API: Schema definition
deactivate Loader

API -> API: Serialize document data\nusing utils.py

API --> Client: HTTP 200 with document JSON
deactivate API

@enduml
